tspan.tspan: Each ribbon of the stream represents a color of part or brick used in LEGO sets.
The width of the ribbon indicates the average number of parts per set each year
that are colored according to the ribbon color. The hex colors provided by LEGO
were used to color the ribbons.
See code and data here: https://github.com/jfaganUK/lego-data
